{
  "stem": "22469.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After this, '41, we got an order from German to leave the village.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they concentrate the Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know why, but they concentrate the Jews in towns and small towns.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the Jews from the villages, they should go-- for example, to Skawina, what was very small town, they concentrate the Jews in Skawina.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my parents and my relation, what we have been all together in this village, Zielonki, they went to Skawina.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my girlfriend with parents also in in Zielonki.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we didn't want to be split.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we married together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "No official, because the official was not allowed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So just according to the Jewish law, [HEBREW]",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Helena.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Helena Pinkas.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So anyway, we went another village, what was not far from Cracow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we'd been in this village until '42 June.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Wola [POLISH]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very small.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very small. 90%, 95%, 98% population, they were Polish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But '42, they would concentrate the outside Cracow people to ghetto Cracow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Again, we didn't know why.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But when we came to this ghetto, in two days, suddenly SS and gestapo surrounded ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they took 5,000 or 6,000 people, and they sent them to the wagons.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But after a few weeks, we find that they went to-- this was-- this was village Belzec.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were built from of the German gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we knew that we going to that.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
